{"tid":1827110,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"武漢新增1人死於新型冠狀病毒肺炎　死者為69歲男子","createTime":"2020-01-16T16:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T17:39:11.000Z","uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1c6e769fb68fcecd59fd675d5655557e6cf115","tid":1827110,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"武漢市衛健委通報，新增1宗感染新型冠狀病毒肺炎的死亡病例，死者是1名69歲男子，上月31日發病，到本月4日病情加重，轉入武漢市金銀潭醫院救治，入院時患有嚴重心肌炎；腎功能異常；多個內臟功能嚴重受損；延至星期三搶救無效死亡。武漢至今累計報告新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎41宗，12人出院，5人嚴重，2人死亡，其餘患者病情穩定，全部接受隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK 2020-01-17 00:26:15"},{"pid":"4749d9b1616146ae11b9d36ae50ed829cb69e129","tid":1827110,"uid":313341,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f69ccb89214e9c43d925e66b7c4844ba8190badf","tid":1827110,"uid":185238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4749d9b1616146ae11b9d36ae50ed829cb69e129","tid":1827110,"uid":313341,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大師"},{"pid":"8cbb5396ef09e1b693f3052e19795e3d352284db","tid":1827110,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f69ccb89214e9c43d925e66b7c4844ba8190badf","tid":1827110,"uid":185238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4749d9b1616146ae11b9d36ae50ed829cb69e129","tid":1827110,"uid":313341,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":